00:15:45,220 --> 00:15:47,920
 That's when we start to wanna conceal or hide.

395
00:15:47,920 --> 00:15:49,160
 And so let me illustrate it this way,

396
00:15:49,160 --> 00:15:50,780
 because I think what a lot of us do

397
00:15:50,780 --> 00:15:51,960
 when we look at our own lives

398
00:15:51,960 --> 00:15:54,240
 is we end up kind of bifurcating our lives.

399
00:15:54,240 --> 00:15:57,200
 We split our lives into two.

400
00:15:57,200 --> 00:15:59,240
 We wouldn't really admit that we do this,

401
00:15:59,240 --> 00:16:01,040
 but really this is what happens,

402
00:16:01,040 --> 00:16:03,180
 is that we think that there's two,

403
00:16:03,180 --> 00:16:05,440
 you think there's two of you and I think there's two of me.

404
00:16:05,440 --> 00:16:08,600
 There's the ideal you and then there's the bad you.

405
00:16:08,600 --> 00:16:12,520
 And the ideal you is the you that really follows this.

406
00:16:12,520 --> 00:16:13,880
 Let's just fill in the blank.

407
00:16:13,880 --> 00:16:17,000
 I should fill in the blank.

408
00:16:17,000 --> 00:16:18,920
 You've got your answers, I've got my answers,

409
00:16:18,920 --> 00:16:21,400
 but the way you answer that and the way I answer that,

410
00:16:21,400 --> 00:16:23,880
 that's what determines the ideal you.

411
00:16:23,880 --> 00:16:27,320
 So I should always be in control of my emotions.

412
00:16:27,320 --> 00:16:30,320
 I should always wanna feel like spending time with Jesus.

413
00:16:30,320 --> 00:16:33,900
 I should always share the gospel every chance that I get.

414
00:16:33,900 --> 00:16:37,040
 I should not feel anxious.

415
00:16:37,040 --> 00:16:39,100
 I should be married right now.

416
00:16:39,100 --> 00:16:41,400
 I should be in a better job right now.

417
00:16:41,400 --> 00:16:45,000
 I should be in a better financial position right now.

418
00:16:45,000 --> 00:16:47,840
 Whatever it is, when you have all of those things lined up,

419
00:16:47,840 --> 00:16:50,840
 you are setting these expectations on your own life,

420
00:16:50,840 --> 00:16:54,000
 saying you should do something.

421
00:16:54,000 --> 00:16:55,520
 And when you do it,

422
00:16:55,520 --> 00:16:58,320
 achieve those little goals that you set out.

423
00:16:58,320 --> 00:17:02,160
 When you do, behave in the way that you think you should.

424
00:17:02,160 --> 00:17:03,880
 That's the ideal you.

425
00:17:03,880 --> 00:17:07,560
 That's the you you like 'cause you're behaving.

426
00:17:07,560 --> 00:17:10,060
 That's the you you think everybody else likes

