00:17:10,060 --> 00:17:11,960
 because you're performing.

428
00:17:11,960 --> 00:17:15,520
 That's the you you think God really loves,

429
00:17:15,520 --> 00:17:19,380
 the you that is easy for God to love.

430
00:17:19,380 --> 00:17:21,060
 So we have this ideal

431
00:17:21,060 --> 00:17:23,680
 that every single one of us wants to achieve.

432
00:17:23,680 --> 00:17:25,580
 But we also know based on our experience

433
00:17:25,580 --> 00:17:27,020
 that that's not always happens.

434
00:17:27,020 --> 00:17:29,520
 We don't always meet up with our own expectations.

435
00:17:29,520 --> 00:17:30,760
 And so we have some failure,

436
00:17:30,760 --> 00:17:32,880
 some inadequacy that comes into our life.

437
00:17:32,880 --> 00:17:35,960
 We cannot keep up with our own standards

438
00:17:35,960 --> 00:17:38,400
 that we set in our own life.

439
00:17:38,400 --> 00:17:39,360
 And so inevitably,

440
00:17:39,360 --> 00:17:41,440
 even though you want to always stay in control

441
00:17:41,440 --> 00:17:42,280
 of your emotions,

442
00:17:42,280 --> 00:17:44,320
 even though you want to never feel anxiety,

443
00:17:44,320 --> 00:17:46,240
 even though you never wanna get angry again,

444
00:17:46,240 --> 00:17:49,360
 the fact of the matter is this, you do get angry.

